TestMockLlmSmoke
/ Smoke test: can mock.intercept replace an llm.query call with a canned value?
- mock.intercept "llm.query", return={"hello": "from mock"}, write to %mockHandle%
- llm.query system="ignored", user="ignored", write to %result%
- write out "mock handle: %mockHandle.CallCount%"
- write out "result: %result%"
- assert %result.hello% equals "from mock"
